StringBuffer vs StringBuilder
---------------------
->StringBuffer is synchronized
-> StringBuilder is not synchronized

->StringBuffer is thread-safe
-> StringBuilder is not thread-safe

->StringBuffer can be used in multi-threaded environment
-> StringBuilder cannot be used in multi-threaded environment


HashTable vs HashMap:
--------------------------------------
->HashTable is synchronized
-> HashMap is not synchronized

->HashTable is thread-safe
-> HashMap is not thread-safe

->HashTable can be used in multi-threaded environment
-> HashMap cannot be used in multi-threaded environment